data.text:

mandsboileeds wrote:

Michelle in corrie is married to Jack ryder who was jamie in Eastenders

Jack Ryder and his co-star Michelle Ryan were rumoured to be very close, way before he met Kym Marsh.

Tamsin Outhwaite and Nigel Harman were a item a few years back. She then went on to marry the guy who recently played Dr. Oliver (Tom Ellis) in Eastenders.

Also Paul Nicholls (Joe Wicks) and Martine McCutcheon were togoether for a while during their Eastenders days as were Gillian Taylforth and Nick Berry!
